    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a superlative example of naturally aspirated precision. Powered by the 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six mated to a tactile 6-speed manual transaxle, this chassis offers an unfiltered connection to the tarmac. The vehicle features Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential for superior cornering dynamics. It has been maintained to a fastidious standard, evidenced by a flawless DME report with zero over-revs in higher ranges and a documented service history including recent coil packs and a transaxle fluid exchange. The exterior retains its factory-original depth, while the Porsche Sport Exhaust (PSE) ensures the mechanical symphony is fully realized. A true turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
